    <intervention_name>Beacon Aqueous Microshunt</intervention_name>
    <description>The Beacon Aqueous Microshunt (BAM) is an implantable device intended to reduce intraocular pressure (IOP) in patients with refractory glaucoma by shunting aqueous humor from the anterior chamber to the surface of the eye.</description>
